query:
SELECT 
  countryId,
  serviceId,
  apiId,
  COUNT(*) as duplicates,
  GROUP_CONCAT(id) as ids
FROM prices
GROUP BY countryId, serviceId, apiId
HAVING COUNT(*) > 1
LIMIT 20;
